| Issue | Severity | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| No security headers | High | Add `helmet` |
| No rate limiting | High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No global error handler | High | Add 404 + error middleware |
| Unauthenticated PII endpoint | High | Add auth middleware |
| No body size limits | Medium | Set `limit` on body parser |
| No input validation | Medium | Add `express-validator`/`zod` |
| Unstructured logging | Low | Use `pino` or `winston` |

