|---|---|---|
| No body size limit | 🔴 High | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| No global error handler | 🔴 High | Add `(err, req, res, next)` middleware |
| No security headers | 🔴 High | Add `helmet` |
| No rate limiting | 🟠 Medium | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No 404 handler | 🟡 Low | Add catch-all middleware |
| No input validation | 🔴 High (future routes) | Use `zod` or `joi` |
